message: "If you use this repository, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "existence-proof: An Empowerment Doctrine for Credential-less AI-enabled Creators — Existence Proof Format, Feasibility-Question Corpus, and Gatekeeping Eval"
version: 0.1.0
date-released: "2026-06-05"
doi: 10.5281/zenodo.20558801
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/shimo4228/existence-proof"
authors:
  - family-names: Shimomoto
    given-names: Tatsuya
